{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/Deriving_the_Quadratic_Formula","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>This page outlines the derivation of the Quadratic Formula.</p>\n<p>We take a quadratic equation in its general form, and solve for x:</p>\n<p>\n  <math>\n    <mtable columnalign=\"left\">\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mo>⁢</mo>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>+ </mo>\n                <mi>b</mi>\n                <mo>⁢</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n              <mo>⁢</mo>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>+ </mo>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n            <mo>⁢</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mi>c</mi>\n          <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>+ </mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>b</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>⁤</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n          <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>-</mo>\n              <mi>c</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Divide out leading coefficient.</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n                <msup>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mi>a</mi>\n              </mfrac>\n              <mo>⁤</mo>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <msup>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mi>b</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                      <mi>a</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mfrac>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mi>c</mi>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n                <mi>a</mi>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>a</mi>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n                <mi>a</mi>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>b</mi>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>a</mi>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Complete the square.</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n              <mo>=</mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>b</mi>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                  <mo>- </mo>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mi>c</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Discriminant revealed.</mtext>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <msup>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>(</mo>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                  <mo>+ </mo>\n                  <mfrac>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mi>b</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                      <mi>a</mi>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mfrac>\n                  <mo>)</mo>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mo>=</mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>b</mi>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                  <mo>- </mo>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mi>c</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>+ </mo>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mi>b</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>=</mo>\n              <msqrt>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>b</mi>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                    <mo>- </mo>\n                    <mn>4</mn>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                    <mi>c</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>4</mn>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>a</mi>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                  </mrow>\n                </mfrac>\n              </msqrt>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>=</mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>-</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n              <mo>±</mo>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>{</mo>\n                <mi>C</mi>\n                <mo>}</mo>\n              </mrow>\n              <msqrt>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>b</mi>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                    <mo>- </mo>\n                    <mn>4</mn>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                    <mi>c</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>4</mn>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>a</mi>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                  </mrow>\n                </mfrac>\n              </msqrt>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">There's the vertex formula.</mtext>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace>\n              <mrow>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>=</mo>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>-</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                  <mo>±</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mo>{</mo>\n                    <mi>C</mi>\n                    <mo>}</mo>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>b</mi>\n                      <mn>2</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                    <mo>- </mo>\n                    <mn>4</mn>\n                    <mi>a</mi>\n                    <mi>c</mi>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n    </mtable>\n  </math>\n</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"This page outlines the derivation of the Quadratic Formula.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-02-18T09:30:25.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Lösungsformel für die Quadratische Gleichung","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MathML: Dériver la formule quadratique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MathML: 二次方程式の解の公式を導く","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MathML: Вывод Квадратичной Формулы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/mathml/examples/deriving_the_quadratic_formula","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/mathml/examples/deriving_the_quadratic_formula/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/303a6c3b8ec6658d2956c191c50aee0a0e9e4da5","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Examples","title":"Examples"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/Deriving_the_Quadratic_Formula","title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula"}],"pageTitle":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}